pitched five scoreless innings in a Triple-A game Wednesday. 
</P>
<P>
	``There won't be nerves ... I'll have excitement,'' said Clemens  
about his start Monday at Oakland. ``I'll have to control my 
excitement early. 
</P>
<P>
