RHP Ricardo Aramboles continues his impressive recovery from major 
offseason elbow surgery. He will likely pitch his first simulated 
game at the Yankees' minor league facility in approximately two 
weeks. ... Yankees minor league catcher Jaime Torres resumed off 
field workouts Wednesday, one week after undergoing thyroid cancer 
surgery. 
