<HEADLINE> Pistons Activate Dumars </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	DETROIT (AP) -- The Detroit Pistons placed guard Charles O'Bannon  
on the injured List Wednesday with right knee tendinitis and 
activated guard Joe Dumars. 
</P>
<P>
	O'Bannon has played in 12 games this season and is averaging 2.8  
points and 1.9 rebounds per game. 
</P>
<P>
	Dumars had been on the injured list since March 22 with a  
strained left calf muscle. He is averaging 11.8 points and 3.2 
assists per game. 
</P>
<P>
	Dumars started at guard for the Pistons against the Boston  
Celtics Wednesday night. 
</P>
</TEXT>
