<CATEGORY> entertainment </CATEGORY>
<HEADLINE> Tom Arnold Files for Divorce </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	LOS ANGELES (AP) -- Actor Tom Arnold and his wife, Julie, have  
filed for divorce after 3 1/2 years of marriage. 
</P>
<P>
	The filing Tuesday in a Los Angeles court cited irreconcilable  
differences and said a financial settlement would be reached later, 
publicist Staci Newman said. 
</P>
<P>
	Arnold, 39, was previously married to comedian and TV star  
Roseanne. That nearly four-year union ended in 1994. 
</P>
<P>
	A year later, he married Julie Lynne Champnella, now 25, in  
Dearborn, Mich. It was her first marriage. The couple have no 
children. 
</P>
</TEXT>
