<HEADLINE> Blue Jays Release Cecil Fielder </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	DUNEDIN, Fla. (AP) -- Cecil Fielder's comeback with the Toronto  
Blue Jays didn't even make it to opening day. 
</P>
<P>
	Fielder, who agreed last month to a minor league contract with  
the Blue Jays, was released today, a day after Toronto acquired 
Dave Hollins from Anaheim. 
</P>
<P>
